from seed.client import SeedNurseryApi

client = SeedNurseryApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",

snippet.async_client:
from seed.client import AsyncSeedNurseryApi

client = AsyncSeedNurseryApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)

    for_="string",
)
